CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 3, 1958, pg. 5A reads: " "Teens 'N' Talent" Participants - These girls were featured in 45-act show sponsored by the All-City Student Council at Schenley High School, April 26. Left to right, standing: Mary Lee Epler, Westinghouse; Clarie Eger, Allderdice High; Bonnie Mohass, South Hills High; Judith Cohen Allderdice High, and Kathy Corcoran, Westinghouse High.  Seated: Pat Wilhelm, Langley High, and Anita Helo, Schenley High. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of "Teen 'N' Talent" participants, from left, seated: Pat Wilhelm and Anita Helo; standing: Mary Lee Epler, Clarie Eger, Bonnie Mohass, Judith Cohen and Kathy Corcoran, posed in hallway of Schenley High School
